tor/home] |- | style="text-align:center;"| ''{{sort|William and Mary Environmental|William and Mary Environmental Law and Policy Review}}'' | style="text-align:center;"| 1975 | style="text-align:center;"| <small>Still active</small> | Began as the William and Mary Journal of Environmental Law in 1975 to report on local and regional topics of [[environmental law]]. Today, the central function of the review is to provide a forum for professors, scholars, practitioners and students to publish articles on current topics of environmental law and examine in a more focused manner the policy implications behind the law. | style="text-align:center;"|<ref>{{cite web|title=Environmental Law and Policy Review |publisher=[[William and Mary Law School]] |url=http://web.wm.edu/law/publications/lawreview/?svr=law |accessdate=July 23, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090625034431/http://web.wm.edu/law/publications/lawreview/?svr=law |archivedate=June 25, 2009 }}</ref> | style="text-align:center;"| [http://web.wm.edu/law/publications/elpr/] |- | style="text-align:center;"| ''{{sort|William and Mary Law Review|William and Mary Law Review}}'' | style="text-align:center;"| 1957 | style="text-align:center;"| <small>Still active</small> | Published entirely by William and Mary law students, it is an annual volume of legal writing containing both professional and student work. | style="text-align:center;"|<ref>{{cite web|title=William and Mary Law Review |publisher=[[William and Mary Law School]] |url=http://web.wm.edu/law/publications/lawreview/?svr=law |accessdate=July 23, 2009 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090625034431/http://web.wm.edu/law/publications/lawreview/?svr=law |archivedate=June 25, 2009 }}</ref> | style="text-align:center;"| [https://web.archive.org/web/20090625034431/http://web.wm.edu/law/publications/lawreview/?svr=law] |}
